network.param.modules.person.vendor

Class Vendor

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.param.modules.person.vendor.Vendor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBean, IPerson, IVendor

    public class Vendor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IVendor
    Implementation of IVendor, this class represents the vendor.

    This interface IVendor will represents vendor information. ICatalogue defines below few categories of operations:

    • setParamID method for set vendor unique ParamID.

    • setTemplateID method for set template id for vendor on boarding.

    • setName method for set vendor name.

    • getParamID method for get vendor unique ParamID.

    • getTemplateID method for get template id for vendor on boarding.

    • getName method for get vendor name.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
